[30;1m27 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m28 | [0m[35m# 1.0.0[0m
[30;1m29 | [0m[35m* massive update - separated functions into separate modules[0m
[30;1m30 | [0m[35m* functions do not accept multiple types anymore - use different versions in their respective module[0m
[30;1m31 | [0m[35m* objects are no longer transformed into functions, simply use `(obj.)` in LiveScript to do that[0m
